flowchart TD
  A[HTTP request\n/assistant/api/message] --> B{Flood checks\nper IP minute/hour}
  B -->|limit exceeded| B1[429 JSON\nRetry-After]
  B -->|ok| C{Validate request\ncontent-type + size + JSON + message}
  C -->|invalid| C1[4xx JSON error]
  C -->|valid| D[Set/validate correlation ID\nSet response header]
  D --> E[Load conversation cache\nilas_conv:uuid]
  E --> F{Repeated-message abuse?}
  F -->|yes| F1[Escalation response + log]
  F -->|no| G[SafetyClassifier]
  G -->|match| G1[Safety refusal/escalation\nviolation tracking + logging]
  G -->|pass| H[OutOfScopeClassifier]
  H -->|match| H1[OOS response + logging]
  H -->|pass| I[PolicyFilter fallback checks]
  I -->|blocked| I1[Policy response]
  I -->|pass| J[Turn classify + Intent route\nquick actions/history fallback]
  J --> K[Early retrieval\nFAQ/resources]
  K --> L[Fallback gate decision\nclarify vs llm path]
  L --> M[Hard-route URL enforcement\noptional response grounding]
  M --> N{LLM enabled + allowed?}
  N -->|no| O[Rule-based response]
  N -->|yes| P[LlmEnhancer call\ncache/circuit/rate/retry/timeout]
  P --> Q[Post-generation safety enforcement]
  O --> R[Persist history + follow-up slot cache\n30m TTL, 10-entry window]
  Q --> R
  R --> S{Conversation logging enabled?}
  S -->|yes| T[Redacted DB write]
  S -->|no| U[Skip]
  T --> V[Analytics + Langfuse trace buffer\nresponse JSON]
  U --> V

  V --> W[Kernel terminate subscriber\nqueue Langfuse export item]
  W --> X[Queue worker on cron\nflush to Langfuse]

  P -->|error path| Y[Exception handling\nSentry tag + Langfuse error + 500 internal_error]
